: 1, male (holotype); 2, male (paratype); 3, female (allotype); 4, female (paratype); 5, head of female (allotype). 6–8: 
<taxonomicName id="4C3D5E917C483176FE3FD691FD04C582" authority="Mitter" authorityName="Mitter" box="[459,740,2015,2036]" class="Insecta" family="Glaphyridae" genus="Pygopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anahitae">
